Refactor libcwd address-to-source-location lookup around an initialization-time cache built from all relevant object files, replacing or rewriting the current dwarf.cc/libdw path so subsequent location_ct lookups are fast, deterministic, and accurate for inline source locations. The implementation should preserve the public location lookup API, modernize symbol/object caching, define any needed explicit initialization entry point, and make location_ct report the call site inside the original inline function body when an address falls in inlined code.
